= Project Narrative

We plan to build an artificial intelligence capable of demonstrating a better ability to predict protein viability by training on similar proteins, and incorporating damaged (but still functional) variants of those same proteins in the training data. Once we are able to predict a protein's mechanism from its structure, we may yet start producing our own custom proteins tailored towards fighting specific diseases and disorders. This offers improvements in quality of life for those affected by the diseases cured, new pharmaceutical jobs, and new opportunities within the pharmaceutical business.
